帕克和斯通在节目播出后得知，部分观众觉得《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》对斯特拉瑟斯的描绘有些过于刻薄。双方虽然没有过直接交流，但帕克和斯通得知，斯特拉瑟斯本是《南方公园》的剧迷，但在看过《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》后非常难过，对剧中有关她的描写有相当情绪化的反应。斯特拉瑟斯感到特别难受的是，她一直在努力帮助那些面临饥饿威胁的孩子，但剧中却把她描绘写窃取孩子食物的伪君子。得知斯特拉瑟斯的反应后，帕克和斯通感到有些后悔，称他们并没有任何指摘她人格的想法。然而第3季的《饿死鬼叭噗上太空》又一次拿斯特拉瑟斯-{zh-hans:开涮; zh-hant:做惡搞對象;}-，并且角色更不讨好，是个类似{{link-en|赫特人贾巴|Jabba the Hutt}}（{{lang|en|Jabba the Hutt}}）的生物。帕克还在《南方公园》{{lang|en|[[数码多功能影音光盘|DVD]]}}的评论音轨中表示：“大姐啊，要是你都那么胖了，还要去太空里谈论什么（忍饥挨饿的儿童）……那你也真太把自个儿当根葱了。我们并不觉得她是个坏人，她可能是一片好心在做这些事情，但拜托上电视前好歹少吃点儿吧。”<ref name="Commentary" />

《[[乡村之声|乡村之声]]》电视评论员汤姆·卡森（{{lang|en|Tom Carson}}）称赞本集中那些“针对美国的富足和健忘的笑话病态到不可思议”<ref>{{Cite news | last = Carson | first = Tom | title = South Park – Gross anatomy of American childhood | work = Newsday | date = 1998-03-15 | location = New York | page = B06}}</ref>。黛安·威廉姆森（{{lang|en|Dianne Williamson}}）在《[[电报和公报|电报和公报]]》（{{lang|en|''Telegram & Gazette''}}）发文，赞扬《饿死鬼叭噗》中对现实生活中原始素材的掌控，称他经常会对《南方公园》主创的勇气感到钦佩<ref>{{Cite news | last = Williamson | first = Diane | work = Telegram & Gazette | title = Sensibility has gone way south; Big media again caves to avoid making waves | date = 2006-03-21 | location = Worcester, Massachusetts | page = B1}}</ref>。[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[拉法叶_(路易斯安那州)|拉法叶]]的《广告商报》（{{lang|en|''The Advertiser''}}）称这是“歇斯底里的”的一集节目<ref name="Advertiser" />，并特别称赞其中对美国消费主义的嘲讽<ref name="Advertiser" />。[[明尼苏达州|明尼苏达州]][[圣保罗_(明尼苏达州)|圣保罗]]的《[[圣保罗先锋报|圣保罗先锋报]]》（{{lang|en|''St. Paul Pioneer Press''}}）认为这集“令人捧腹”<ref name="SaintPaul">{{Cite news | title = Turkey and TV | work = St. Paul Pioneer Press | location = [[圣保罗_(明尼苏达州)|Saint Paul]], [[明尼苏达州|Minnesota]] | date = 2004-11-25 | page = A15}}</ref>，还称“我们知道自己不该笑，但就是忍不住”<ref name="SaintPaul" />。[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]《[[信使邮报|信使邮报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Courier-Mail''}}）的维姬·英格伦（{{lang|en|Vicki Englund}}）称赞节目“实在匪夷所思的故事情节”<ref name="Englund">{{Cite news | last = Englund | first = Vicki | work = The Courier-Mail | date = 1998-08-17 | title = TV Reviews | location = Queensland | page = 24}}</ref>和其中的寓意，并且特别欣赏有关斯特拉瑟斯的笑料：“观看爆笑的下半集时最好别吃东西，其他的毋须多言”<ref name="Englund" />。

《[[奥兰治县纪事报|奥兰治县纪事报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Orange County Register''}}）评论员沃恩·佩里（{{lang|en|Vern Perry}}）称《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》是他最喜欢的《南方公园》剧集<ref name="OCR1113">{{Cite news | last = Perry | first = Vern | title = Not just another pretty face | work = The Orange County Register | date = 1998-11-13 | page = F33}}</ref>。1998年，《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》发文总结《南方公园》如此受观众欢迎的十大原因，本集便是其中之一<ref>{{Cite news |last=Johnson |first=Allan |title=Guilty pleasures: 10 reasons to watch the unlikely, and unseemly, hit "South Park" |date=1998-02-08 |work=Chicago Tribune |location=[[芝加哥|Chicago]] |accessdate=2015-10-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20151016151713/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-02-08/news/9802080482_1_south-park-guilty-pleasures-christmas |deadurl=no |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1998-02-08/news/9802080482_1_south-park-guilty-pleasures-christmas |archivedate=2015-10-16 |page=C17 }}</ref>。2003年，《芝加哥论坛报》又将这集评为《南方公园》最有趣的十集之一<ref>{{Cite news |last=Johnson |first=Allan |title=Whoever thought this show would last 100 episodes? |date=2003-04-09 |deadurl=no |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-04-09/features/0304090091_1_south-park-music-teacher-comedy-central |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130119021434/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2003-04-09/features/0304090091_1_south-park-music-teacher-comedy-central |newspaper=Chicago Tribune |location=Chicago |page=C1 |archivedate=2013-01-19 }}</ref>。比尔·沃德（{{lang|en|Bill Ward}}）在《[[明星论坛报|明星论坛报]]》（{{lang|en|''Star Tribune''}}）撰文称，《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》是卡特曼“最出彩的半小时”<ref>{{Cite news | last = Ward | first = Bill | title = Critic's choice | work = Star Tribune | date = 1999-03-10 | location = Minneapolis | page = 12E}}</ref>。当然，并非所有媒体都对节目持正面评价。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》撰稿人马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）就批评《南方公园》“低俗且欠成熟”，《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》更是令人特别反感<ref>{{Cite news | last = Gilbert | first = Matthew | title = Cute but crude, sly kids can kick "Butt-head" | date = 1998-01-28 | work = The Boston Globe | location = Boston | page = D1}}</ref>。布赖恩·博伊德（{{lang|en|Brian Boyd}}）也在《[[爱尔兰时报|爱尔兰时报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Irish Times''}}）发文，指责本集将正在挨饿的非洲儿童作为取乐的资本<ref>{{Cite news | last = Boyd | first = Brian | title = Comedy from the edge: Bart's a brat, and Beavis and Butthead are puerile slime, but the eight-year-old anti-heroes of the latest animation series from the US are really offensive | date = 1998-03-28 | work = The Irish Times | location = Dublin | page = 64}}</ref>。

1998年11月，《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》和《南方公园》另外11集的{{lang|en|DVD}}套装发布。套装共有3碟，本集同《[[圣诞便便，黄金先生|圣诞便便，黄金先生]]》、《[[机械怪兽史翠珊|机械怪兽史翠珊]]》（{{lang|en|''Mecha-Streisand''}}）和《[[隆鼻手术_(南方公园)|隆鼻手术]]》（{{lang|en|''Tom's Rhinoplasty''}}）一起收录在第3碟<ref name="OCR1113" />。1998年发行的{{lang|en|[[VHS|VHS]]}}录像带套装《南方公园假日特别节目》（{{lang|en|''South Park Festival Special''}}）一共收录了6集《南方公园》，除《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》外，另外5集分别是《圣诞便便，黄金先生》、《[[圣诞快乐，查尔斯·曼森|圣诞快乐，查尔斯·曼森]]》（{{lang|en|''Merry Christmas, Charlie Manson!''}}）、《[[黄金先生的圣诞经典歌曲|黄金先生的圣诞经典歌曲]]》（{{lang|en|''Mr. Hankey's Christmas Classics''}}）、《[[Korn解开海贼幽灵之谜|Korn解开海贼幽灵之谜]]》（{{lang|en|''Korn's Groovy Pirate Ghost Mystery''}}），以及《[[结膜炎病毒_(南方公园)|结膜炎病毒]]》（{{lang|en|''Pinkeye''}}）<ref>{{Cite news | title = Our competition could cause anarchy | date = 2000-12-19 | work = Grimsby Evening Telegraph | page = 12}}</ref>。2002年11月12日，《南方公园：第一季完整版》（{{lang|en|''South Park: The Complete First Season''}}）的{{lang|en|[[DVD|DVD]]}}发布，其中收录了第1季包括《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》在内的13集节目<ref>{{Cite news | last = Lawson | first = Terry | title = 4-disc "Rings" could take up a whole weekend | work = Detroit Free Press | date = 2002-11-12 | location = [[底特律|Detroit, Michigan]]}}</ref>。帕克和斯通为每集都录制了评论音轨，但由于其中某些语句涉及的“标准”问题而未纳入{{lang|en|DVD}}，两人都不接受{{lang|en|DVD}}收录这些音轨所需要的剪辑和审查，最终所有评论音轨都是经{{lang|en|CD}}单独发行<ref>{{Cite news | last = Owen | first = Rob | title = "South Park" warped and worthy | work = Pittsburgh Post-Gazette | date = 2002-11-22 | location = Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania | page = 39}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | last = Pratt | first = Doug | title = Doug Pratt's DVD: Movies, Television, Music, Art, Adult, and More! | year = 2005 | publisher = UNET 2 Corporation | isbn = 1-932916-01-6 | page = 1123}}</ref>。从2008年开始，观众还可以通过官方网站免费在线观看包括《-{zh-hant:餓死鬼叭噗; zh-hans:饿死鬼叭噗; zh-tw:感恩節，四賤客領養「ㄅㄚˇㄅㄨ」;}-》在内的每一集《南方公园》<ref>{{Cite news | title = Sweet, "South Park" is free online | date = 2008-03-26 | work = The Boston Globe | location = New York City, New York | accessdate = 2015-09-29 | archivedate = 2014-11-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141104014224/http://www.boston.com/business/technology/articles/2008/03/26/sweet_south_park_is_free_online/ | url = http://www.boston.com/business/technology/articles/2008/03/26/sweet_south_park_is_free_online/}}</ref>。

